headline: Caesars Palace Times Square to Fund High-Tech EMS Ambucycle™ Program: Innovative Lifesaving Response Model To Dramatically Reduce Emergency Response Times Set to Come to Hell’s Kitchen and West Midtown
summary: NEW YORK, July 28, 2025--Today, Caesars Palace Times Square announced an unprecedented partnership with United Hatzalah, a volunteer-based emergency medical service organization, to launch its 24/7 Ambucycle™ EMS response program in Hell’s Kitchen from 40th to 53rd Street and 6th to 10th Avenue, if awarded a gaming license from the State of New York at the end of the year.
